{
  "stem": "2916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We are going to play football with the heads of Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We'll cut their heads off and play football with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And to me, this was so terrifying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I couldn't sleep, because I'd visualize bloody heads of the local people in my town rolled on the ground.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had a large football field in-- in Samorin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I visualized them playing football with the heads of Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was terrifying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when I told my father about it, I was crying, and I couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he said, oh, don't take that literally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is just Hitler wanting to raise the anger and hostility against Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it's only figurative speech.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's not literal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You-- you didn't have to be a prophet to realize that these things were going on around us and that we are heading for doom.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The only thing that would have saved us is an early Allied victory over Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And unfortunately, Hungary was occupied by Germany quite late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when I say unfortunately, I meant to say that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Unfortunately, 1944 when already the Allies landed in Western Europe, the Americans landed in Western Europe, that was the time when we were deported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So, the Allied victory didn't save us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, which I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- it's not even puzzling to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because, you see, by the time the deportation reached us, it was so well-organized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was systematic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was quick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People were immediately registered Jews and rounded up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And within three weeks, we already were gone from our hometown into a ghetto in another town, under strict military police supervision.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no time to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Also, you see, where we live is a flat area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's called the Small Danube Plain, plain, flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
